* 2015-09-14 21:36PM this program will print generate a 3 * 3 matrix
* 11 12 13
* 21 22 23
* 31 32 33

TYPES:
  BEGIN OF line,
    col1 TYPE i,
    col2 TYPE i,
    col3 TYPE i,
  END OF line,
  itab TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF line WITH EMPTY KEY.

